{"tid":1078787,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"搵工心得：你要做到工搵你。","createTime":"2019-03-26T13:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T15:50:14.000Z","uid":193614,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4ccc2179f2f1d7d838ebd606fd0ab336db17ea","tid":1078787,"uid":193614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"搵工心得。 唔岩做就唔好做, 唔好以為得以條路先係出路。 仲有盡快決定係唔係要轉工。有D人做二個幾三個月就想resign 其實好晒時間。 我自己為例 <br />\n我前前後後係以個幾月做左幾份工。 最後搵到一份我真係敢心命地去長做既。<br />\n搵工最重要既係 <br />\n1.同事既氣氛<br />\n2.工作量 <br />\n最好初入行既 搵D 多trainees or 新人既公司<br />\n禁樣起頭好快上手又快適應整個環境。<br />\n以家我份工 同事上司係超好 工作量又唔算太多<br />\nSenior 好樂意教人，career path 算好清晰。<br />\n加油 各位搵工"},{"pid":"60f7c0d9559350f4ebd7fbc21399195fbb3f07b2","tid":1078787,"uid":176601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:27:25.000Z","msg":"邊行？"},{"pid":"3eb916d6ac16a991258a5477d11b484d3ba035a2","tid":1078787,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:37:18.000Z","msg":"咪又係金融狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13374b55dcb262c14121cc356682f375e9f93ff8","tid":1078787,"uid":193614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3eb916d6ac16a991258a5477d11b484d3ba035a2","tid":1078787,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:37:18.000Z","msg":"咪又係金融狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"我講緊點樣搵工 唔好意思"},{"pid":"a835ea27a026363cb7031b8dacde92229278b66a","tid":1078787,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:50:14.000Z","msg":"咁撚害死人 <br />\n<br />\n唔係行行都可以quit. 完快速搵下份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}